    <div class="pgh-PageHero_Inner">
      <div class="pgh-PageHero_Body">
        <h1 class="pgh-PageHero_Title pgh-PageHero_Title-large ani-Animation_SlideUp">About us</h1>
        <h2 class="pgh-PageHero_Subtitle ani-Animation_SlideUp">We are an interdisciplinary research centre within the University of Cambridge dedicated to the study and mitigation of existential risks</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  
    

<section class="sec-SplitImageText" >
  
  <div class="sec-SplitImageText_Inner">
    <div class="sec-SplitImageText_Body">
      <a href="/contact/" class="sec-SplitImageText_Content">
        <h2 class="sec-SplitImageText_Title">Existential risks in the 21st Century</h2>
        <p class="sec-SplitImageText_Text">Now is an important time for efforts to reduce existential risk. There are new and largely unstudied risks associated with powerful emerging technologies and the impacts of human activity, which in the worst case might pose existential risks. We want to reap the enormous benefits of technological progress while safely navigating these catastrophic pitfalls. These threaten everyone – we can only tackle them together.</p>
        
          <div class="sec-SplitImageText_Link">Get in touch</div>
        
      </a>
      <a target="_blank"  href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3qF26MbYgOA" class="sec-SplitImageText_Image">
        
          <div class="sec-SplitImageText_VideoIcon"></div>
        
        
          <div class="img-Image js-LazyImage"
     data-alt-text=""
     data-aspect-ratio="56.27476882430648%"
